--------------------
PRE-REQUISITS
--------------------

+ OpenCV
	- ./configure --prefix=/usr/intel
	- make && make install
	- adjust /etc/ld.so.conf or appropriate /etc/ld.so.conf.d/file.conf
	- ldconfig -v


+ YConfigFile
	- make
	- no install :-(	




--------------------
INSTALL
--------------------

- No autoconf support yet
- change Makefile to reflect install paths of OpenCV and YConfigFile 
- make


